Class STIntersectBlockReader

            • org.apache.lucene.codecs.uniformsplit.sharedterms.STIntersectBlockReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Accountable, BytesRefIterator

    public class STIntersectBlockReader
extends IntersectBlockReader
    The "intersect" TermsEnum response to STUniformSplitTerms.intersect(CompiledAutomaton, BytesRef), intersecting the terms with an automaton.
    WARNING: This API is experimental and might change in incompatible ways in the next release.
